data.description: Stunning 1-story home boasts an open floor plan with 9’ ceilings, creating an airy & inviting atmosphere. The luxurious gas stove is perfect for preparing gourmet meals. Extra-large kitchen is adorned with quartz counters & stainless-steel appliances with a spacious walk-in pantry. The oversized island offers ample space for meal prep & entertaining guests. Tile flooring throughout the main living areas adds a touch of elegance, bedrooms feature plush carpets. Primary bedroom features beautiful wood & glass closet doors, adding a touch of sophistication. The ensuite bathroom has a lavish tub. Laundry room, complete with a washer & dryer, offers generous storage space. The garage offers room for a small third car or additional storage. Low-maintenance yard with desert landscaping provides ease of care. MORE PICTURE COMING THIS WEEK.
